September manufacturing HSBC purchasing managersâ€™ index.  The Manufacturing PMI is designed to provide a single figure
snap-shot for Turkish manufacturing. It is designed to provide
the most up-to-date picture of business conditions in the
private manufacturing sector. Anything above 50 indicates expansion;
below 50, a contraction. The greater the divergence from 50, the
